  "id": "RAW_cc00a2c4",
  "title": "广州厂商做的一款“淡淡”的模拟经营，怎么就登顶美国手游榜了？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&mid=2650676153&idx=2&sn=ab537d5889ed76b08cd7324c502c051c",
  "date": "2025-12-24 13:31:00",
  "author": "白鲸出海",
  "siteName": "白鲸出海",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 2 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 4px;border-color: rgb(53, 175, 253);min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503192481\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dRE5QVKQvKa1FXYHjAVMbQgS8OHicibvOvuGRyOg43LhDrCQrqIuIQtJGiaA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"555\" data-cropsely2=\"312\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd409739&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dRE5QVKQvKa1FXYHjAVMbQgS8OHicibvOvuGRyOg43LhDrCQrqIuIQtJGiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">看似没机会的玩法，找对切入点也能拥有高人气。</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: right;justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -1px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 1px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(134, 147, 155);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">封面图片由AI生成</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">出品</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 8px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 2 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">｜白鲸出海编辑部</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 8px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 2 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">作者</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 8px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 2 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">｜</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">B21993</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 40px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今年，出海厂商跑出成绩的品类，主要集中在 2 个，SLG 和休闲（主要是合成）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 40px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">虽然我们也发现同样有许多厂商在模拟经营上发力（详见文章《</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&amp;mid=2650675680&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=4350d9e34625a106bb4c66e8663ce2a0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"上线一个月 DAU 破万，聚集成都的模拟厂商正探索下一个爆款密码\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">上线一个月 DAU 破万，聚集成都的模拟厂商正探索下一个爆款密码</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">》），但总体来说在最重要的美国都还没做出什么成绩；上一个进入美国手游榜 Top 5 的产品还是益世界旗下融合 RPG 玩法的「Isekai：Slow Life」，但也已经是至少 2 年前的事情。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503192482\" data-ratio=\"0.6328205128205128\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"975\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e7f291d7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dREo6ReQEdjcLDUECDEhHjev5uQ8jVzg3zOxHl2yLnJumSg93OEdRWgTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">「My Leisure Time」美国市场正式</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">上线首日登顶 iOS 手游榜，iOS 总榜</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">跻身 Top 2 | 数据来源：点点数据</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 40px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但就在 2025 年就要过去的时候，一款名为「My Leisure Time（ 中文名“我的休闲时光”）」的出海新品打破了僵局。同样是模拟经营的玩法，但正式上线首日就登顶美国 iOS 手游下载榜，在 iOS 总榜也跻身 Top 2。它做对了什么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503192483\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.69921875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"768\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1bd873a5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dREChADQLRe86Pcic0icb7y7whlKzhmBoH974rrC6jtt5wyJke1TVDLrHFQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px 40px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">「My Leisure Time」| 图片来源：点点数据</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:614px !important;margin-top:0px;height:auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">曾经爬上中国台湾 Top 5，</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">进入欧美市场找准“Cozy Game”标签</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503192484\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4637223974763407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1268\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4d537209&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dREN1H89gdnngLw6MpPDiatI8IWPg8l0GlWoGQj4rD18t4WhWENmEY3vtw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503192485\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.272655634357762\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1269\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=81abe629&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dREHRl89NRPVaosMGEzgmfYRDWiawJ6E4CnVdfOicf9VePIib62BGzegSUTg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">中国内地 iOS 和小游戏版「我的休闲时光」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">的发行账号名为“Skydream”（天之梦游戏，</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">上图）；打开其在 App Store 所留下的客服</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">地址能看到，游戏的软著授权人是广州卓</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">动信息科技有限公司 | 图片</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-weight: normal;\">来源：Skydreams CO., LTD</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">data.ai 显示，「我的休闲时光」首先在 2024 年 3 月于中国内地 App Store 上线，不久后也上线了小游戏版本。游戏在国内的发行账号为“天之梦游戏 （Skydreams）”，账号官网显示游戏的软著授权人是广州卓动信息科技有限公司。在 12 月 24 日 DataEye 发布的《2025年中国小游戏 100 强企业榜》中，广州卓动位居第 52 位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503192486\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26871552403467297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1269\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b38db49c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dREnIEskJTUV35Qib1L1qny8an33kzXAVvayUWzLrN50nGFWJh8Riczf13A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">在面向海外市场的英文版上线前，</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">「我的休闲时光」已经在中国香港、中国</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">澳门以及中国台湾上线，广大大记录数据显示</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">游戏曾经进入中国台湾 iOS 下载</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">总榜 Top 5 | 数据来源：data.ai</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">之后，「我的休闲时光」在 2025 年 3 月于中国香港、中国澳门以及中国台湾等市场上线。据广大大观察，游戏曾在中国台湾跻身 iOS 下载总榜 Top 5。随后英文版又在 10 月率先于欧美 Google Play 商店预热，最终在 12 月 23 日于双端正式上线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">和大部分模拟经营产品一样，「我的休闲时光」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">的主要内容就是让玩家装修房屋，然后挂机</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">积攒装修资源“金币”，从而购买更多家具来进</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">一步装饰和升级自己的家园 |&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">视频来源：My Leisure Time</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">从玩法上看，「我的休闲时光」的确贯彻了“休闲”一词，主要为放置模拟经营。主人公厌倦了压抑的大城市，搬到了名为“悠悠镇”的小镇上。玩家的任务就是设计装修房屋，通过挂机搜集资源来不断购买家具和扩建房子，让主角过上恬淡的乡村生活并结交新朋友。游戏的画风也主打温馨可爱、甚至有点手绘风格，软萌的 Q 版人物配合各种暖色调配色，的确让人看着清新温暖。海外版本也延续了国内休闲、温馨，利用休闲时间玩一会的定位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503192487\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7226162332545312\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1269\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d1152793&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dREjWsfotxmvRq3giaEut7kX9hpwfsgTibNWSOzKzeB241qB0NiasBibw2amw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">购买家具装修房间，是「我的休闲时光」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">的主要内容 | 图片来源：My Leisure Time</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而这样一个定位的游戏，在美国登顶游戏榜，其实是令人意外的。观察后，我们发现除了单纯的大力投放素材买量之外，游戏本身也切入了一个在欧美人气很高的游戏子类——Cozy Game（可以翻译为“惬意游戏”）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503192489\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5233333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1200\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=42379a74&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dREg28uFN0tCRZ0YCaqvicIxLWib9ibyoTft41bOwxjNQK1F2h0YmOV7cM2w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">以「星露谷物语」为代表的慢节奏</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">模拟经营游戏，是“Cozy Game”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">的典型案例 | 图片来源：Polygon</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">什么是 Cozy Game？Gemini 的回答显示，Cozy Game 的核心在于不以“赢”为目的，而以“感受”为核心。从数值难度上讲，这类游戏给玩家的压力很低；从玩法上看，主要以种田、装修、社交等追求“体验”的机制为主；从画风和配乐上看，也是追求色彩柔和音乐舒缓。这类玩法的崛起原因很复杂，但主要来自于部分玩家厌倦头部 3A 游戏追求的强对抗机制、或现在的手游的商业化浓度，亦或是玩家在经济下行环境下寻求安全感的表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503192488\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40189125295508277\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1269\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1bf54821&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dREH69RYPkDb7xZDNAx5GUibAano6KibfDQfCbuI932a23cFY7QfPfcyODg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">目前 Reddit 上 CozyGamers 分区成员</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">总数已经达到 23 万人 | 图片来源：Reddit</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Cozy Game 玩家主要聚集在 Reddit 等社区，也会在 YouTube 等视频平台上分享新游戏。目前 Reddit 上 Cozy Game 讨论区“CozyGamer”的成员已经超过 23 万人，YouTube 上分享 Cozy Game 的视频观看量也往往能够上万。可以看出，「我的休闲时光」完全符合 Cozy Game 的定义，游戏在 Facebook 主页和 YouTube KOL 的合作文案里点明了自己就是最新款 Cozy Game；借助对欧美玩家偏好的敏锐洞察，广州卓动瞄准了一个此前国内厂商很少涉足的新用户群体，完成了起量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503192490\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43854166666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=69e9d82d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVtXFGEetwicSyNDo4NM9dRELWQt3UZ6nkhPJsXBsvgfAScTO8Tpe0Iy9Ghxbt1NTMqrGfF3ZXRhYg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178)